::Prowl::

Prowl nods. -Sure thing, but please be carefull in the battle.- He 
kisses Iron Raptor before rising several dozen more feet, clearing 
the trees.

-I'll slow down several dozen miles away from the CF so you can get 
reoriented,- Prowl thinks to her, his boosters flaring up. In several 
seconds, they were approaching 400mph. He sees Shadow Cat and Snow 
Tech up ahead, and in two seconds him and Iron Raptor were past the 
two cats, leaving them far behind. 




--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, "Megan Solmonson" <tmrattrap@h...> wrote:

ground,

Fire.>

her hands

>

that,

with as
